messages.subject: Thanks for having me!
messages.msgSnippet: I want to thank everyone here for your input and for opening my mind to different things in the short time I have been here. I am unsubscribing from the group
messages.messageBody:
I want to thank everyone here for your input and for opening my mind to
different things in the short time I have been here. I am unsubscribing from
the group and wish you all the best in your unschooling ventures.

I don't believe that homeschooling the unschooling way is for me. I will
continue with my venture in homeschooling, just not in this way.

Dee
